------------------
FY_FightYard_CS666
------------------

Created by root666of666evil, CS666 clanleader.
This is my very first CSS map, took me 5 days to make this map
and learn sdk from scratch, and I have much left to learn,
there are some minor bugs but nothing gameplay disturbing,
nevertheless I think this map is very enjoyable.
I will probably release an update in the nearby future.

If you would like to try this map online please visit my server:
ServerIP: 62.105.225.126:27015
Servername: [NL] CS666 Close - Combat


-------------
INSTALLATION:
-------------
cache file --> cstrike/maps/soundcache
ain file --> cstrike/maps/graphs
bsp file --> cstrike/maps
nav file --> cstrike/maps
start CS:source, open console, type "FY_FightYard_CS666", press ENTER.


-----
INFO:
-----
Created by: root666of666evil
Contact: root666of666evil@hotmail.com
Release Date: March 18/2005
Capacity: 10vs10 (20)
Works with Bots: Yes, not exactly perfect but its ok.

--------------
To all admins:
--------------
Feel free to host this map on your server, as long as you
include this readme and I get the propper credits.
There is a nice pit just outside the map where you can teleport/drop
anyone who gives you any trouble ~8)
exactly 100 spikes awaiting on impact, after a nice long fall ;)

--------
Credits:
--------
Special thanks to the the entire CS666 team for testing
this map and the constant flow of ideas and support
(dark666angel, dice666of666death, varangian666guard,
spawn666of666satan, priest666of666satan, jack666herrer,...)
